# Space Trucker – Project Overview

A survival-focused space cargo sim where you haul weird cargo through a handcrafted galaxy. Inspired by Euro Truck Simulator, Death Stranding, and Freespace — minus combat.

- ✴️ No combat
- 💀 Death is dangerous and taboo
- 🪐 Galaxy is handcrafted and story-aware